  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of DM

          -  Must have the symptoms of pain or numbness

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient with pregnancy (or child bearing potential),or in lactation

          -  Patient currently taking concomitant TCM medications.

          -  Patient with Drug or alcohol addiction

          -  Patient with medical history of myocardial infarction, cerebro-vascular disease, major
             trauma, operation 6 months prior to enrollment

          -  Patient with liver dysfunction (SGOT or SGPT&gt;2x ULN)

          -  Patient with renal insufficiency (serum creatinine&gt;1.3mg/dL)
      </textblock>
